1) Create the tables course, with fields:
- course_id of type integer,
- course_name of type varchar2 having the size of 50
- course_description of type varchar2 having the size of 100.

mysql> CREATE TABLE course (course_id int, course_name varchar(50), course_description varchar(100));

2) Add the field, course_day of type varchar2 of 50.
mysql> ALTER TABLE cours ADD course_dayVARCHAR(50);
mysql> SHOW table;



mysql> CREATE DATABASE school;
